      "title": "Fire breaks out at Union Place apartment",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "COLOMBO (News 1st); A fire has broken out in the 04th floor of an apartment complex in Union Place, Colombo 02 on Tuesday (16).",
        "The Fire Department stated that 03 service vehicles have been dispatched to curb the fire.",
        "The Colombo Fire Department also stated that the fire has been brought under control now.",
        "The department confirmed that no one was injured in the fire.",
        "Sri Lanka asked China to delay Yuan Wang 5, until it addressed India\u2019s concerns"
